1. *Sprat* je imao dvadeset tri sobe. (The floor had twenty-three rooms.)
2. U dvorištu je bio jedan *sprat*. (In the yard there was one floor.)
3. Na kraju se nalazi *sprat* sa prostorijama za goste. (At the end there is a floor with guest rooms.)
4. U zgradi je bilo pet *spratova*. (In the building there were five floors.)
5. Posetili smo četvrti *sprat*. (We visited the fourth floor.)
6. Na ulazu je bilo napisano da je zgrada imala tri *sprata*. (At the entrance it was written that the building had three floors.)